author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
MARVEL Cosmic Invasion launches December 1st on Steam, Nintendo Switch 2, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation and Xbox consoles!

Play the Steam demo and wishlist it now: https://www.dotemu.com/games/marvel-cosmic-invasion/

War spreads amongst the stars but fire and life incarnate still prevail!

The X-Men formerly known as Marvel Girl uses her massive telekinetic powers to crush the insectoid invaders, but that is not all: The flames of the Phoenix are ready to consume all manners of evil!

Bug soldiers better beware: the Invincible Iron Man has also joined the battle! Whether it’s firing mighty repulsor blasts or powering up the Iron Cannon, Tony Stark’s jet-powered alter ego brings all of his technological might to Annihilus’ doorstep!

Phoenix and the Invincible Iron Man join and complete MARVEL Cosmic Invasion’s incredible lineup featuring Captain America, Wolverine, Spider-Man, Storm, Phyla-Vell, Venom, Nova, She-Hulk, Rocket Raccoon, Silver Surfer, Beta Ray Bill, Black Panther, and C
title: MARVEL Cosmic Invasion | Release Date Trailer

description:
This week on The Official Marvel Podcast, we’re joined by Supervising Sound Editor Jonathan Greber to explore the sound design behind Marvel Animation’s latest project, Marvel Zombies (2:24). Plus, we dive into all the spooky-themed content coming to Marvel Games, including Marvel Rivals and Marvel Snap with Phil Cooper and Tom Tao from Marvel Games (14:03). All time codes are approximate.
